d 'URTABLE': module to perform ADF, DF-GLS, PP, and KPSS unit-root tests with data-driven lag/bandwidth selection
d
d      urtable reports four unit-root and stationarity tests on a
d single time series in one    comparison table: the augmented
d Dickey-Fuller (ADF), the Elliott-Rothenberg-Stock   
d GLS-detrended DF (DF-GLS) in three variants based on different
d lag-selection criteria,    the Phillips-Perron (PP), and the
d Kwiatkowski-Phillips-Schmidt-Shin (KPSS) test. All lag    lengths
d and bandwidths are chosen data-driven. The output table includes
d critical values    at 1%, 5%, and 10%, decision flags, and a
d one-sentence conclusion at the 5% level that	  aggregates the
d evidence across the four tests. 
d
d KW: unit root
d KW: ADF
d KW: DFGLS
d KW: PP
d KW: KPSS
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260522
d
d Author:  Y. Baris Altayligil,  Istanbul University, Department of Economics
d Support: email  ybaris@@istanbul.edu.tr
d
f urtable.ado
f urtable.sthlp
